com.skratchdot.electribe.model.esx

Interface PartWithSample

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    PartDrum, PartKeyboard, PartStretchSlice
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PartDrumImpl, PartKeyboardImpl, PartStretchSliceImpl, PartWithSampleImpl

    public interface PartWithSample
    A representation of the model object 'Part With Sample'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Reverse
    • Sample Label
    • Sample Pointer
    • Start Point
    • Reserved Bits After Reverse

    See Also:
    EsxPackage.getPartWithSample()
